Package com.ibm.mobile.services.core.http

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IBMHttpRequest
    IBMHttpRequest contains all the information that is needed in order to invoke an HTTP request to a secured endpoint.
    IBMHttpResponse
    IBMHttpResponse is the result obtained from making an IBMHttpRequest.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IBMHttpException
    The IBMHttpError class is a provisional API.
    IBMMutableHttpRequest
    IBMMutableHttpRequest provides the ability to configure and make HTTP requests.
